{"baseRefName":"main","baseRefOid":"e4542eb3cfcaaa9604cfc8fd74b178093bad0fc0","body":"## Summary\n\n- recognize source-first translation requests such as `любая формальная система либо неполна, либо противоречива - translate to english`\n- route Rust and browser requests through the shared source → language-neutral meaning → target pipeline\n- add the reported proposition in English, Russian, Hindi, and Chinese, plus all 12 directed round-trip assertions\n- prevent UTF-8 cache-key truncation panics and stop `система` from being misread as the Russian theme command `тема`\n- declare the Agent CLI test model's context limits so OpenCode does not compact away its report turn\n- add a patch-release changelog fragment for the automated release pipeline\n\n## Root cause\n\nTranslation routing only accepted actions at the beginning of English/Russian prompts, while the unquoted extractor ignored seed forms whose slot appeared before the action suffix. The formalization and browser paths repeated those assumptions. In the web app, substring matching also found `тема` inside `система`, so the main thread intercepted the reported prompt before the worker saw it.\n\n## Reproduction and verification\n\nBefore this change, the reported prompt returned the unknown-answer fallback. It now returns:\n\n`any formal system is either incomplete or inconsistent`\n\nAutomated coverage includes:\n\n- exact Rust integration reproduction\n- parser, formalization, and Unicode cache regressions\n- every directed pair among en/ru/hi/zh through one shared meaning\n- Chromium coverage for the exact prompt, four target renderings, and the theme-command collision\n- the unchanged four-turn Agent CLI report/recall/follow-up scenario (9 chat rounds)\n- full local `cargo test --all-features`: 152 integration, 481 source, and 1,802 unit tests passed; 2 exhaustive tests ignored by the normal suite\n- `cargo fmt --check`, Clippy with warnings denied, seed sync, file-size, hardcoded-language, i18n, language-parity, and intent-coverage checks\n\nThe complete issue/PR capture, CI logs, timeline, root-cause matrix, requirements, and primary-source research are indexed in [the evidence bundle](https://github.com/link-assistant/formal-ai/blob/issue-776-d6f207d7c577/dev/log/issues/776/pulls/794/README.md).\n\n## Visual evidence\n\nNo screenshot is included because this is routing/translation behavior rather than a visual layout change; the browser behavior is covered by Playwright.\n\nFixes #776\n","commits":[{"authoredDate":"2026-07-19T05:10:44Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-07-19T05:10:44Z","messageBody":"Adding .gitkeep for PR creation (default mode).\nThis file will be removed when the task is complete.\n\nIssue: https://github.com/link-assistant/formal-ai/issues/776","messageHeadline":"Initial commit with task details","oid":"9191515e8d5b39b6ef13e56aa45535f863955681"},{"authoredDate":"2026-07-19T06:34:58Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-07-19T06:34:58Z","messageBody":"","messageHeadline":"test: reproduce source-first translation failure","oid":"5e9ea5cf5f29ab9f88a006c53b759aa5ac970f51"},{"authoredDate":"2026-07-19T06:35:36Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-07-19T06:35:36Z","messageBody":"","messageHeadline":"fix: support source-first multilingual translation","oid":"26d701eb2e502de54a34cd6deb9df11586703844"},{"authoredDate":"2026-07-19T06:36:03Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-07-19T06:36:03Z","messageBody":"","messageHeadline":"docs: preserve issue 776 investigation logs","oid":"684653238e46364846ef23173c361e45dce7cf32"},{"authoredDate":"2026-07-19T06:36:20Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-07-19T06:36:20Z","messageBody":"","messageHeadline":"chore: normalize collected issue logs","oid":"2757c8f537e5f5928138baaf2768d8b2d7b8bcd4"},{"authoredDate":"2026-07-19T06:36:37Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-07-19T06:36:37Z","messageBody":"","messageHeadline":"Merge remote-tracking branch 'origin/main' into issue-776-d6f207d7c577","oid":"e4f415b6ffd44c34ce337e2916a24afaadd4c9a5"},{"authoredDate":"2026-07-19T06:39:36Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-07-19T06:39:36Z","messageBody":"","messageHeadline":"docs: record post-merge verification","oid":"483497bea311ddbd46b444a5dd1f63ad717991e6"},{"authoredDate":"2026-07-19T06:42:34Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-07-19T06:42:47Z","messageBody":"","messageHeadline":"fix: defer version bump to release automation","oid":"ab2fd90ac97b6360671ec49fd6bae32e4da7d801"},{"authoredDate":"2026-07-19T06:55:52Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-07-19T06:55:52Z","messageBody":"","messageHeadline":"fix: stay within worker mirror budget","oid":"c5d699b8a59662172056f5df9e149c06f29c1414"},{"authoredDate":"2026-07-19T07:01:31Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-07-19T07:01:31Z","messageBody":"","messageHeadline":"test: prevent agent cli report compaction","oid":"2765db8368c8df0d55f2ad6e3208eb3d9b5b8685"},{"authoredDate":"2026-07-19T07:18:52Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-07-19T07: